            "code_var_name": "body_force_b",
            "description": "The body force (e.g., gravitational or inertial force) acting within the domain, appearing in the weak form of elastostatics.\nJUSTIFICATION:\nThe body force b is introduced in the elastostatics weak form as a source term, and is integrated over the domain with the test function v.",
