            "code_var_name": "function_space_V",
            "description": "The function space of test functions, which must be chosen to satisfy the boundary conditions and is used in the weak formulation.\nJUSTIFICATION:\nThe space V is repeatedly referenced as the space of test functions, with the requirement that the weak form holds for all v \u2208 V.",
