        "test_function_v": {
            "code_var_name": "test_function_v",
            "description": "A test function used in the weak formulation, belonging to the function space V, and is varied over the domain to enforce the variational equation.\nJUSTIFICATION:\nThe variable v appears in multiple weak formulations as the test function, with the requirement that the bilinear form B(u,v) holds for all v \u2208 V.",
